# Description
# This file is the PPP file for the following modem:
# 		Skywire LTE CATM1 Verizon Modem: NL-SW-LTE-SVZM2x (SVZM20-ES, SVZM20)
#
# Instructions
# 	1. 	You will need to add your APN in the file: vzw-SVZM2x-chat
# 	2. 	This file is setup for PPP using the NL-M1DK. If you are using another product,
#		change the line:
#			/dev/ttyUSB0
#		to however the Skywire enumerates for you.
#
# Note: We recommend flow control at this high of baud rate, which is why we added the
#   crtscts
# option

/dev/ttyUSB0
921600
connect "/usr/sbin/chat -v -f /etc/ppp/peers/vzw-SVZM2x-chat"
noauth
crtscts
defaultroute
usepeerdns
local
debug
updetach
